<br>
60 vs 60 you will lose if he has even elementary pvp knowledge.  There's nothing you can really do about it other than hope his isp bogs down and lags him out so you can kite him.  Maybe you can chain click those shaman instaheal pots if you have the cash.  Primal axe/shovel of the harvest/etc caliber weapons will leave you in HTdisc deathtouch range after one decent double attack if he scrubs your buffs with a golem wand first.<br>
<br>
As a dark elf on vallon zek I had the good fortune to meet up with the uberguild equipped erudite sks and the pointlessness of it was an inspiration to mages everywhere.  <br>
<br>
