<br>
High level SK's with the discipline can kill a caster in 1 HT, after a scrubbing with a golem wand.  Instant, unresistable, no other spells or sword whacks required.<br>
<br>
Probably the only way to beat an SK is to have so much HP gear that they waste their HT without killing you, and that you then have enough time to run around and regen with your phantom armor line.<br>
<br>
So the best policy for SK's is to just avoid them.  Even a trained monkey with a 60 SK should be able to defeat any veteran PvP caster.<br>
<br>
